4
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:21,720
People often get confused about how to address the topic of pricing.

5
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:27,420
The starting point, really, is to look at who our customer is

6
00:00:27,420 --> 00:00:30,000
and their point of view.

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,920
Do they consider us to have a differentiated value proposition?

8
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:37,960
Do we have a real point of difference?

9
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:42,160
Or are we quite similar to everybody else?

10
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:44,510
If we've got a real point of difference, it

11
00:00:44,510 --> 00:00:49,100
will typically come out in our brand and our extended offering.

12
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:56,561
And if we don't, then they will see us being quite similar to our competitors.

13
00:00:56,561 --> 00:00:57,060
If

14
